text: Tatyana Vladimirovna Dolmatova (, ; born 14 September 1992) is a footballer who plays as a midfielder for Shirak-Homenmen. Born in Russia, she represents the Armenia women's national team. ==International career== Dolmatova capped for Armenia at senior level in two friendlies against Lithuania on 4 and 6 March 2020. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Russian women's footballers Category:Russian Women's Football Championship players Category:Russian emigrants to Armenia Category:Naturalized citizens of Armenia Category:Armenian women's footballers Category:Armenia women's international footballers
